OL,5, An elderly woman who suffered a broken 
OL,6, eye socket and a bleed on the brain    
OL,7, when she was knocked down by an        
OL,8, e-scooter rider has told of her ordeal.
OL,10,FMyra Wood, 79, was walking near her    
OL,11,Fhome in Bexhill when Paul Satchell, 58,
OL,12,Fcrashed into her while he was trying to
OL,13,Fevade police on 1 December 2020.       
OL,15,FHe admitted causing serious injury by  
OL,16,Fdangerous driving at Lewes Crown Court 
OL,17,Fand was jailed for 16 months.          
OL,19,FTwo years on, Mrs Wood said she was    
OL,20,Fstill "absolutely petrified".          
